# Key Considerations

- Proper caching configuration improves performance and reduces cost
- CloudFront can restrict direct access to S3 using Origin Access Control (OAC)
- HTTPS should be enabled for secure content delivery
- Cache invalidations may be required after updating content

---

## Why It Matters

CloudFront is widely used to improve scalability, performance, and security for modern cloud applications and static websites.
